# Nova — Telegram Personality Bot (Gemini)

A Telegram bot powered by Google Gemini free tier that chats with a hardcoded personality ("Nova" — witty, warm, slightly sarcastic).

## Setup

### 1. Get your keys

| Key | Where |
|-----|-------|
| **Telegram Bot Token** | Message [@BotFather](https://t.me/BotFather) on Telegram → `/newbot` → copy the token |
| **Gemini API Key** | https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey → Create API key (free tier) |

### 2. Configure

```bash
cp .env.example .env
```

Edit `.env` and paste in your two keys.

### 3. Install dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 4. Run

```bash
python bot.py
```

The bot will start polling Telegram. Open your bot in Telegram and send it a message!

## Commands

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `/start` | Introduce Nova & reset conversation |
| `/reset` | Wipe chat history and start fresh |

## Changing the personality

Edit the `PERSONALITY` string in `bot.py` — that's the system prompt sent to Gemini for every conversation.
